      <abstract>
        <p>Bath &amp; Body Works is featuring clear glycerin with candy corn-colored soap kernels floating inside; photo (Pulse column: Halloween Special) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Having your mouth washed out was never this much fun. Bath &amp; Body Works, the cosmetics chain, features clear glycerin bars with candy corn-colored soap kernels floating inside. They're $5 each from a selection of Halloween-theme soaps.</p>
        <p>For adults, there's body lotion in a pumpkin-shaped pump, $11.50.</p>
      </block>
